WEBVTT

00:07:59.051 --> 00:08:02.313
na baadhi ya wachapa magazeti wakiita
haya matukio "Ununuzi na fujo,"

00:08:02.337 --> 00:08:05.125
ambayo pengine inaeleza
kwa maneno ya utafiti wetu.

00:08:05.673 --> 00:08:07.149
Oh! -- tunaenda nyuma.

00:08:09.730 --> 00:08:11.186
Sawa, hatua ya tatu.

00:08:11.210 --> 00:08:13.027
Mwishowe, mpinduzi yupo eneo lake,

00:08:13.051 --> 00:08:17.623
na anataka kuepuka
kukamatwa na polisi.

00:08:17.647 --> 00:08:20.348
Wapinduzi wataepuka
polisi muda wote,

00:08:20.372 --> 00:08:22.466
lakini kuna usalama kwenye wengi.

00:08:22.490 --> 00:08:25.551
Na kwa upande mwingine, polisi,
na rasilimali zao kidogo,

00:08:25.575 --> 00:08:28.154
wanajaribu kulinda jiji
kadri watakavyoweza,

00:08:28.178 --> 00:08:30.191
kukamata wapinduzi inapowezekana